data.description: Come and see this cozy split level conveniently located  off of Ashley Phosphate, making it an excellent investment opportunity. This wonderful home is located just minutes from shopping, restaurants, craft breweries, as well as numerous city parks. Quick access to I-26 & Dorchester Road, makes navigating the Charleston Metro a breeze. Be in Downtown and or the beaches in minutes.This property is also a perfect opportunity for any investors!Don't hesitate, schedule your showing today!
